reviewText:
Purchased these used as a group; I wasn't sure if they would be o.k.
I was pleasantly surprised. All of the movies work like new,
By buying VHS and used Disney movies....I saved so much $. New DVD's cost anywhere from 19.99 to $50.00 for classics.
My son will watch these over &'over, then maybe I will be able to sell these cheaply to a Amazon & help a parent to get like I was helped.
